title: tcharding
author: tcharding
content: Anyone on the Central Coast interested in starting a meet up with me? Anywhere from Hornsby to Newcastle really. I was thinking of holding it in a park near a beach with a BBQ, my first choice would be JDs in Norah Head.Bitcoin only, it would be nice if it could be technical but we probably have to extend to anyone interested in Bitcoin not just devs.Cheers.
